                     <interp inst="t18481218-266-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 288 lbs. weight of iron, value 20<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18481218-name-284" type="victimName">
